{"tid":1485853,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"講句公道話，留守派同「冷氣軍師」都有好嘅一面，唔洗互屌，應體諒","createTime":"2019-08-18T16:54:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T17:13:00.000Z","uid":56146,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"befc8fc802584829eca8a51530c19ee77813f637","tid":1485853,"uid":56146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:54:18.000Z","msg":"一方面留守派前線想殿後，一齊走，用行動證明齊上齊落。當中亦有人唔想咁快完，叫囂發洩，做吓創作，圍內面對面討論前境等等。前線一直都有哨兵睇路，該散就會散<br />\n<br />\n另一方面「冷氣軍師」（包括行完返屋企嘅手足）擔心狗一發癲，到時又失幾個兄弟就唔好。而且過往經驗一入夜就好危險，加埋鬼嘅存在，擔心到屌出聲都唔奇。<br />\n<br />\n如果咁諗，各位條氣會唔會順啲？仲有好長嘅路，各位手足要互惠互諒互助互信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />記住核爆都唔割。"},{"pid":"f72904693b917fe82e6eb282239966c58dac03ef","tid":1485853,"uid":56146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:57:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d6299add1ed94f6104c6e84805bff05caa5f710","tid":1485853,"uid":56146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:58:26.000Z","msg":"兄弟爬山，各自努力<br />\n<br />\n小弟文筆差，希望你哋明我意思"},{"pid":"b7541239e12206f66fa9e9483bec8457277b1aba","tid":1485853,"uid":56146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:58:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aeb7d8ebf318ee232d1f486054a8b91de9250e1c","tid":1485853,"uid":56146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:59:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\